name: Brain Zaps II
description:
This piece is part of a series of mine (Chaotic Mind , 2022).

-

"A sudden jolt of electricity, like someone had just zapped my brain. I paused, confused, as the odd sensation continued. It felt like my head was being filled with static, like I was stuck in the middle of a bad TV reception. I shook my head, trying to dispel the weird feeling, but it only got worse. I felt disoriented, like I was in a dream. I didn't know what was happening to me."

-

Abstract light-painting created with steel wool on fire in pitch darkness. It was complemented by digital art.

*

'Brain Zaps II', 2022
